Best druid cheal ratio/HPsec: 7.8 ratio 382 HPsec<br>
Best cleric cheal ratio/HPsec: 18.75 ratio 612 HPsec<br>
<br>
Best druid large fast heal ratio/HPsec: 3.5 ratio 467 HPsec<br>
Best cleric large fast heal ratio/HPsec: 4.6 ratio 733 HPsec<br>
<br>
Best druid fast heal ratio/HPsec: 3.5 ratio 467 HPsec<br>
Best cleric fast heal ratio/HPsec: 3.6 ratio 829 HPsec<br>
<br>
Yes, druids aren't clerics.  2 druids using all their mana and effort can match 1 cleric, healing wise.  Druids are bad healers -- 2nd best in the damn game, but still bad compared to clerics.<br>
<br>
