<br>
And yes, this &quot;problem&quot; should shrink as you go to a more and more powerful guild.  More 2nd box clerics, more clerics recruited because they are the single largest raid bottleneck in the game, and the like mitigate this problem for groups.<br>
<br>
An alternative would be to increase group size, to spread the thin clerics over more ground.  =p<br>
