<br>
We aren't hating on you because you are the 2nd best healers in the game.<br>
We aren't hating on you because you are the only class that ports other than us.<br>
We aren't hating on you because you are in the top three nukers.<br>
We aren't hating on you because you are also one of the better buffers.<br>
We aren't hating on you because you are one of the best DoT'ers in the game.<br>
<br>
We, and I mean more than just wizards, think that druids simply don't need the increase in power.  You as druids are the 2nd or 3rd best at a large list of things, basically allowing you to fill several different roles in a group.  You may not do them as well, but you shouldn't be able to, otherwise you might as well break out the pencils, paper, and dice and start playing RIFTS.  It's the difference of one spell line that can turn the class from balanced to being a munchkin class.<br>
<br>
Druids already do have a bad rep with many wizards, I'll admit that.  But this isn't about wizards being annoyed by how good such a versatile class is at nuking and tp'ing, while those wizards don't think that the difference should be as small as they are for damage dealing.  I think I speak for most of the people here when I say all this.  I wouldn't care if they came up with a line of slows for druids if they weren't as good as the current slowing classes.  Druids just don't need better heals. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=930.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=930.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=930.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=930.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=930.topic&start=101&stop=102>6</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=930.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=930.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=930.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.threadControl?topicID=930.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/the